Re: Colloquial translation issues
by Hyperworm » Tue 11.16.2010 4:57 pm It can be hard to find information on slang, even with a search function at hand (which is working fine I think - I tried ちゃう).Your questions may have been posted before, but there's nothing wrong with asking anew if you can't find answers. ^^;(Ask in here? )
